										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Exploring Microsoft Azure and all it&#8217;s great features starts with the registration for a free trial account.<br>With this free trial account you get started with 12 months of <em>free</em> services, 40+ services that are always <em>free</em>, and USD200 in credit. To sign up for a free trial account register <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free">here</a></p>



<p>Select Start free</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="891" height="396" src="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-33" srcset="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-1.png 891w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-1-300x133.png 300w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-1-768x341.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 891px) 100vw, 891px" /></figure>



<p></p>



<p>Sign-in/Sign-up for a Microsoft account using an email address and password.<br>if you don&#8217;t have a Microsoft account select create one next to No account?<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="440" height="337" src="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35" srcset="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-3.png 440w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-3-300x230.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px" /></figure>



<p>Enter your Country/Region and your Date of Birth<br>click next<br>you will receive a verification code on the email address you provided. Enter this code <br>click next<br><br>Fill in the captcha you see on your screen<br>click next</p>



<p>If the information you provided is correct you will be redirected to the Azure Sign-up page. <br>Enter your Region your Name and phone number and your email address (newly created or used for signup)</p>



<p>Next you will need to verify your phone number. <br>Click text me or call me. Enter the verification code you received.<br><br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="725" height="373" src="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-4.png" alt="" class="wp-image-36" srcset="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-4.png 725w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-4-300x154.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 725px) 100vw, 725px" /></figure>



<p>Next enter your payment details. You will need a creditcard (Mastercard/Visa/American Express).<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="391" height="430" src="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-5.png" alt="" class="wp-image-37" srcset="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-5.png 391w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-5-273x300.png 273w" sizes="(max-width: 391px) 100vw, 391px" /></figure>



<p>Make sure you check the boxes for the Terms and conditions and click Sign Up.<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="373" height="293" src="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-6.png" alt="" class="wp-image-38" srcset="https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-6.png 373w, https://ldecuba.github.io/techblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/image-6-300x236.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 373px) 100vw, 373px" /></figure>



<p>You have finished registration and created a free Microsoft Azure account.<br>You also have a balance/Azure spend of 200$ USD.</p>
